item.title: WWE 2K18 Rhyno ECW TV and ECW World Champion
item.media:title: WWE 2K18 Rhyno ECW TV and ECW World Champion
item.media:description:
Here is a screenshot of Rhyno titles history.

The first title that Rhyno won in the WWE was ECW World Television Championship. (ECW is part of the WWE.) He won it on April 8, 2000 on ECW from Yoshihiro Tajiri. He loss the title to Kid Kash on August 26, 2000 on ECW.

He won the title again from Kid Kash on September 9, 2000 on ECW.

On January 7, 2001 at Guilty as Charged Rhyno won the ECW World Heavyweight Championship from The Sandman.

Rhino was the final wrestler to hold both of the ECW World Television Championship and ECW World Heavyweight Championship till April 11, 2001. ECW closed on April 4, 2001.

Note: Why wasn't the ECW titles on the line during "WWF VS. The Alliance" story?

WWE 2K18 © Yuke's and Visual Concepts
Screenshot taken from WWE 2K18 on Xbox One.

Total: 12RP (Common)

 Character  
Gender: Female
Name pronunciation: Hip-hee
Name origins: the song "Hiphopopotamus vs. Rhymenoceros" by Flight of the Conchords
Relationships:
Caoba - Handler.
Personality: Hiphy is a jokester and sack equally filled with energy and apples. She's a great horse for starters, but extremely hot-headed and excitable with her main rider, Caoba. She's a very social mare, and will stick with other mares and fillies. She doesn't like hanging out with most stallions, however she can make exceptions. She's influential, if other horse spooks she will too. Even if she loves you and appreciates you, she'll swat you with her tail and sometimes try to bite or kick, but when you ride her everything changes. Hiphy is silent but expressive and loves to meet pets and animal she's never seen before.
Quirks: Loves to eat lots of apples and sweet potatoes. She loves baths and is easy to groom but she's terrified of blankets and gunshots. She usually swims out of the saddle and has little knowledge of personal space.
History: Caoba found Hiphy when he reached adulthood traped and freezing to death in a river. He got in the frozen river himself to pull her out and used magic to save her life. Caoba brought Hiphy back to her herd, but they met again when she was grown. Her body grew tough, even for a young mare. She followed him until he decided to adopt her. Since then they do everything together, and both of them would give their life to protect the other.
Alignment: Lawful Good

item.title: Daily Fakemon Day 67 - Rhythermo
item.media:title: Daily Fakemon Day 67 - Rhythermo
item.media:description:
Rhynomite
Rhino Pokemon
Fire-type

Ability - Anger Point / Bulletproof / Flash Fire (Hidden)

Rhynomite have extremely short tempers, headbutting everything within close proximities until they collapse with exhaustion. People are warned to stay far away from Rhynomite in their natural habitat because they will charge at anything they are unfamiliar with.


Rhythermo
Locomotive Pokemon
Fire/Steel-type

Ability - Anger Point / Bulletproof / Flash Fire (Hidden)

Their skin is extremely sturdy, effectively making them bulletproof. Their huge horn expells a molten-like substance which keeps them from overheating and effectively acts similarly to an exhaust of a car, making them move faster. They were once critically endangered, but after conservation in the Savarla Plains their numbers have increased tenfold. 

Evolution line
Rhynomite -- Level 40 --> Rhythermo



Orbis region and all content is (c) to me and is not available for public use


Adopted from NachtBeirmann
